## Conclusion

This project shows how machine learning can be used to forecast retail sales and support business decision-making. By combining historical sales data with store information, promotions, holidays, oil prices, and transaction activity, the model can identify important sales patterns and generate useful future sales predictions.

The project also demonstrates how Python and Power BI can work together: Python is used for data preparation and machine learning, while Power BI is used to communicate results through interactive visual reports.

